        "title": "AT&T said Trump's tax cut would create jobs – now it's laying off thousands of workers",
        "content_html": "<p>Since the coronavirus pandemic began, the telecoms giant AT&amp;T has announced permanent closures of hundreds of retail stores around the US and laid off thousands of workers.</p> <a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/business/2021/mar/30/at-and-t-tax-cut-job-layoffs-store-closed\">Continue reading...</a>",
